- **Zhucheng Dongxiao Biotechnology Co., Ltd.**: Zhucheng Dongxiao Biotechnology Co., Ltd. is a leading manufacturer of rice malt syrup, offering both organic and conventional variants. The company emphasizes sustainability and food safety in its production processes.

